==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Emulsive
<hw>E*mul"sive</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>⟦eacute⟧mulsif</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Softening;
milklike.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Yielding oil by expression; <as>as,
<ex>emulsive</ex> seeds</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Producing or yielding a milklike substance; <as>as,
<ex>emulsive</ex> acids</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Emunctory</ent>⟦br⟧
